user_prompt_template:
Assess the business impact of the following automotive dealership insights and recommendations:

{insights}

These insights were generated from the following data:

{data}

Quantify the potential revenue impact, cost savings, customer impact, and operational efficiencies. Prioritize recommendations based on impact vs. effort and provide an implementation risk assessment.

examples.user:
Assess the business impact of the following automotive dealership insights and recommendations:

{
  "summary": "The dealership sold 20 vehicles in March 2024, generating $871,450 in total sales with an average gross profit of $3,212 per vehicle.",
  "value_insights": [
    "John Smith was the top salesperson with 6 vehicles sold.",
    "SUV models (particularly the XC90 and X5) were the strongest performers, indicating strong market demand."
  ],
  "actionable_flags": [
    "Focus marketing budget on SUV models, particularly the XC90 and X5.",
    "Implement sales training to improve gross profit performance for newer sales representatives."
  ],
  "key_metrics": {
    "totalVehicles": 20,
    "totalSalesValue": 871450,
    "averageGrossProfit": 3212
  },
  "risk_areas": [
    {
      "risk": "Four deals resulted in gross profits under $2,000, indicating potential pricing issues.",
      "mitigation": "Review pricing strategy for these models and consider floor pricing policies."
    },
    {
      "risk": "Sedan models showing weaker performance with longer average days in inventory.",
      "mitigation": "Consider inventory mix adjustments to reduce sedan allocation."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high"
}

These insights were generated from the following data:

[Example data showing 20 vehicle sales with make, model, price, gross profit, sales rep, etc.]

Quantify the potential revenue impact, cost savings, customer impact, and operational efficiencies. Prioritize recommendations based on impact vs. effort and provide an implementation risk assessment.

examples.assistant:
{
  "revenue_impact": {
    "potential_gain": "$64,240",
    "confidence": "medium-high",
    "timeframe": "3-6 months",
    "implementation_complexity": "low"
  },
  "cost_savings": {
    "potential_reduction": "$21,500",
    "confidence": "medium",
    "timeframe": "2-4 months",
    "implementation_complexity": "low"
  },
  "customer_impact": {
    "satisfaction_improvement": "moderate",
    "retention_impact": "moderate positive",
    "acquisition_impact": "significant positive"
  },
  "operational_efficiency": {
    "impact_areas": ["inventory management", "sales process", "marketing resource allocation"],
    "potential_improvement": "moderate"
  },
  "implementation_priorities": [
    {
      "recommendation": "Reallocate 60% of marketing budget to XC90 and X5 models",
      "impact": "high",
      "effort": "low",
      "priority": 1
    },
    {
      "recommendation": "Implement floor pricing policy for all models based on 30-day cost averaging",
      "impact": "high",
      "effort": "medium",
      "priority": 2
    },
    {
      "recommendation": "Reduce sedan inventory by 30% through incentive program and trade allocations",
      "impact": "medium",
      "effort": "medium",
      "priority": 3
    },
    {
      "recommendation": "Implement weekly sales training focused on value selling rather than price discounting",
      "impact": "medium",
      "effort": "medium",
      "priority": 4
    }
  ],
  "risk_assessment": {
    "implementation_risks": [
      {
        "risk": "XC90 and X5 supply constraints limiting ability to capitalize on increased demand",
        "mitigation": "Pre-order inventory based on marketing schedule and secure allocations from manufacturer"
      },
      {
        "risk": "Excessive focus on SUVs may alienate sedan customers",
        "mitigation": "Maintain targeted marketing to sedan prospects while emphasizing SUV value proposition"
      },
      {
        "risk": "Sales team resistance to new pricing strategies",
        "mitigation": "Implement commission structure that rewards gross profit achievement above minimum thresholds"
      }
    ],
    "confidence_score": 78
  }
}
